@startuml
title Lifecycle - Capability Intent to Commit

[*] -[#FB8C00]-> Emitted : script emits intent
Emitted -[#FB8C00]-> Routed : route via ctx channel
Routed -[#FB8C00]-> Batched : queue by layer/channel
Batched -[#FB8C00]-> Reconciled : merge + reconcile
Reconciled -[#FB8C00]-> Evaluated : run optional evaluator predicates
Evaluated -[#E53935]-> Rejected : detect invalid conflict/dependency/evaluator rejection
Rejected -[#E53935]-> [*] : panic-fast abort
Evaluated -[#43A047]-> Committed : apply world mutations/events
Committed -[#FB8C00]-> [*] : frame complete
@enduml
